{"tid":1061304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母躲廁所產子　脖子纏布丟垃圾袋狠心離開","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:20:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce9da0e60fb89067d788d5e01f66e34e5923ed2","tid":1061304,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"越南壯奔縣工業區一間公司，工人在廁所發現一個黑色垃圾袋，裡面有個體重約3.2公斤重的新生兒。<br />\n據《<a href=\"http://BAOMOI.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBAOMOI.com&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhppugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=5b53cb62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">BAOMOI.com</a>》網站報導，3月11日下午5點左右，工業園區一家公司的工人，在廁所的黑色垃圾袋內發現新生兒。目擊者指出，是一名母親在廁所產子，並用布綁在嬰兒的脖子上。目前已經報警請警方調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190314/640_9590ce38dbb50fd5911b8c49bc9127ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190314%2F640_9590ce38dbb50fd5911b8c49bc9127ff.jpg&h=6f681314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190314/640_d16e4cae8514eac0f351af4a25195e1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190314%2F640_d16e4cae8514eac0f351af4a25195e1a.jpg&h=b2f42ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190314/640_31cbc7239a42eca172dcd164a01d6845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190314%2F640_31cbc7239a42eca172dcd164a01d6845.jpg&h=ca5bd1af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190314/640_18a2dcfdf86b1e2f2c68f1277e46a36f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190314%2F640_18a2dcfdf86b1e2f2c68f1277e46a36f.jpg&h=d9ccb925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190314/640_